How can I be responsible for him?

28
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,080
You can.

29
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:03,800
Of course you can.

30
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,840
Don't trap yourself in lies.

31
