Listen to me. Listen.

97
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,800
You're a good woman.

98
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,560
I'm the useless one.

99
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:18,000
I'm the one who failed you.

100
